{"tid":2016500,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"畀人鬧我都要講: sigma, 其實你好自私","createTime":"2020-05-14T12:01:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T06:07:51.000Z","uid":76115,"like":30,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8bc87fcacd333078c587c1df397440831fa856f6","tid":2016500,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:01:45.000Z","msg":"創辦二次元解密係你一個人嘅成就, 你叻, 我地欣賞你<br />\n但係呢個台行到而家, 經歷過處決電競雞, #weplaywelearn改變香港一整代教育生態, 宣傳李小龍健身哲學造就一代前線, 今時今日佢已經變成something bigger than you, something not only about you<br />\n就好似美國建國之後, 呢個國家嘅state-building就唔再只係關一班獨立宣言簽署人嘅事, 係一個群體嘅事<br />\n你已經兩星期冇出新片, 我而家同你講, 如果你真係想放棄教育香港人嚴密邏輯, 匡正香港社會風氣呢啲使命, 唔緊要, 你講聲, 呢條路我地會幫你行落去<br />\n尼采, 一個我會叫佢做德國sigma嘅哲學家講過: One repays a teacher badly if one always remains nothing but a pupil. 沒有sigma, 我們什麼都不是, 但係如果你要掉低二次元解密去沉迷你嘅花花世界, 咁好對唔住, 我地條路就同你行到去呢一到。"},{"pid":"add8d6d8aa51538adc924cfe2d743d17f822d8e1","tid":2016500,"uid":194326,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:03:21.000Z","msg":"佛利民有冇同sigma做過愛"},{"pid":"66c98f2b6a754c45bfd5e7a35d8973d541f213d8","tid":2016500,"uid":87394,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:05:46.000Z","msg":"洋文個段可唔可以翻譯下🙏🏻"},{"pid":"5a7434cd347775ffbf83ef52cf2e618590eb5f05","tid":2016500,"uid":42848,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"有冇咁痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72e307fa6785e5c0e35a57b506a2960562a3719","tid":2016500,"uid":60434,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"Pr狗 拉"},{"pid":"42142660fbf19b3cb6f2ea1ea14364d51913243f","tid":2016500,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"who is 尼彩 ？"},{"pid":"57f445e790c44ecd573b10f50aae3cce05107c2f","tid":2016500,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep